  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Capital Alliance, CT CLSA win top Sri Lanka\u2019s CFA capital market awards",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT  \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s Capital Alliance and CTCLSA Securities have carried away top capital market awards given by the Chartered Financial Analysts\u2019 chapter in the island, the organization said.",
        "Capital Alliance Securities Private Ltd was awarded Gold for the Best Stockbroking Research Team, CFA said. Asia Securities Private Ltd was awarded the Silver, while CT CLSA Securities Private Ltd received the Bronze award",
        "Capital Alliance and also got the award for the Best Sector Report.  Asia Securities Private Ltd and Capital Alliance Securities Private Ltd share the Bronze award. The Silver award was not presented.",
        "CT CLSA Securities got the Gold award for the Best Equity Research Report. Capital Alliance Securities Private Ltd won both the Silver and the Bronze awards.",
        "Sunshine Holdings PLC got the Gold for Best Investor Relations. The Silver was won by National Development Bank PLC. Dialog Axiata PLC and John Keells Holdings PLC share the Bronze.",
        "Expolanka Holdings PLC under was commended for improved investor relations practices over the past year.",
        "Senfin Money Market Fund was named the the Best Unit Trust Fund. JB Vantage Short-Term Gilt Fund won the Silver. The Bronze award was not presented."
      ],
